	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>feasibility of having a game editor run on the SNES itself</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I had this idea earlier today of having a cart with a large amount of battery save RAM, and a small amount of ROM, allowing you to edit itself.  It could have a graphics editor, a level editor, and the ability to animate the enemy and object behavior frame by frame, like an animated cartoon.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


